  You can add files to the staging area then move them over into commits

What are some situations when branches would be helpful in keeping your history
organized? How would branches help?

  Branches would be helpful by adding code into your project without breaking.

How do the diagrams help you visualize the branch structure?

  You can tell when each branch was developed so you see the whole overview of the entire project.

What is the result of merging two branches together? Why do we represent it in
the diagram the way we do?

  all of the commits are merged into one branch. It is showing the merged commits.

